instructions.step_5_output:
Create a markdown file using 'output.filename_template' and save to 'output.output_folder'. Use this structure per paper:

## {number}. {Paper Title}

**Authors:** {formatted author list}
**arXiv:** [{paper_id}](https://arxiv.org/abs/{paper_id})
**Categories:** {paper categories}

{abstract or summary depending on mode}

---

instructions.step_6_header:
At the top of the file include:

# arXiv Daily Digest — {date}

**Mode:** {mode}
**Categories:** {comma-separated categories}
**Keywords:** {comma-separated keywords}
**Papers found:** {count}
